1
00:00:44,400 --> 00:00:45,600
She is not my wife.

2
00:00:45,840 --> 00:00:46,680
What she is wearing

3
00:00:46,680 --> 00:00:48,480
is my wife's skin.

4
00:01:17,800 --> 00:01:19,360
My wife!

5
00:01:30,920 --> 00:01:31,720
This...

6
00:01:45,039 --> 00:01:45,840
My wife.

7
00:01:49,400 --> 00:01:52,060
So not all the people in Luoxian Town are locals.

8
00:01:52,200 --> 00:01:53,520
That's what it means.

9
00:02:07,880 --> 00:02:09,400
Spider-Man?

10
00:02:10,560 --> 00:02:11,800
Anti-gravity?

11
00:02:16,000 --> 00:02:17,560
Why did you expose it?

12
00:02:17,720 --> 00:02:19,440
Why did you expose it?

13
00:02:19,720 --> 00:02:20,720
Madam.

14
00:02:21,880 --> 00:02:24,600
What exactly are you, madam?

15
00:02:24,960 --> 00:02:26,090
Protect the master.

16
00:02:30,960 --> 00:02:31,620
Be careful.

17
00:02:40,880 --> 00:02:41,920
Madam.

18
00:02:41,920 --> 00:02:43,160
Madam.

19
00:02:43,600 --> 00:02:45,120
Madam,

20
00:02:46,240 --> 00:02:49,520
what exactly are you, madam?

21
00:02:50,160 --> 00:02:51,000
Notice updated.

22
00:02:51,000 --> 00:02:52,000
Monster updated.

23
00:02:52,040 --> 00:02:52,760
Corpse Puppet.

24
00:02:52,760 --> 00:02:53,720
Rules updated.

25
00:02:53,720 --> 00:02:56,240
The transformed Corpse Demon is indistinguishable from a normal person before awakening,

26
00:02:56,240 --> 00:02:57,760
unless triggered by a keyword.

27
00:02:57,760 --> 00:02:59,000
Weaknesses: Fire and sunlight.

28
00:02:59,000 --> 00:02:59,640
I see.

29
00:02:59,640 --> 00:03:00,400
I told you

30
00:03:00,400 --> 00:03:03,330
there's definitely something wrong with this town.

31
00:03:06,400 --> 00:03:06,800
Madam.

32
00:03:06,800 --> 00:03:08,120
She is no longer your wife.

33
00:03:08,120 --> 00:03:09,160
This is a Corpse Demon,

34
00:03:09,160 --> 00:03:10,840
crafted from a stolen body.

35
00:03:11,240 --> 00:03:12,520
It hasn't fully developed yet.

36
00:03:12,520 --> 00:03:13,400
Otherwise,

37
00:03:13,400 --> 00:03:14,960
it can only be destroyed by True Sun Fire.

38
00:03:14,960 --> 00:03:15,560
Lin Mo,

39
00:03:15,760 --> 00:03:16,360
remember,

40
00:03:16,560 --> 00:03:17,440
you owe me one.

41
00:03:17,640 --> 00:03:18,960
Find your second and third brothers.

42
00:03:18,960 --> 00:03:20,800
We have work to do tonight.

43
00:03:21,560 --> 00:03:22,360
Wait.

44
00:03:23,200 --> 00:03:24,920
You cannot enter the Lin Manor without an invitation.

45
00:03:24,920 --> 00:03:25,520
Also,

46
00:03:25,720 --> 00:03:28,650
there are other non-human entities in Luoxian Town.

47
00:03:28,840 --> 00:03:29,840
I'm telling you this for free.

48
00:03:29,840 --> 00:03:30,700
We are even now.

49
00:03:30,920 --> 00:03:31,680
Thanks.

50
00:03:31,920 --> 00:03:32,680
Let's go.

51
00:03:41,400 --> 00:03:41,880
Madam.

52
00:03:41,880 --> 00:03:42,680
Village Head.

53
00:03:42,760 --> 00:03:44,560
I know you are very sad right now,

54
00:03:44,960 --> 00:03:46,880
but I have other questions to ask you.

55
00:03:46,880 --> 00:03:48,010
Stop torturing him.

56
00:03:48,120 --> 00:03:49,000
What do you want to know?

57
00:03:49,000 --> 00:03:49,800
I'll tell you.

58
00:03:52,120 --> 00:03:52,760
Fine.

59
00:03:53,560 --> 00:03:54,420
Village Chief,

60
00:03:54,840 --> 00:03:56,970
please hurry and lay your wife to rest.

61
00:03:57,320 --> 00:03:58,380
It's getting dark.

62
00:03:58,520 --> 00:03:59,980
Let's go to my house first.

63
00:04:09,880 --> 00:04:10,880
Master Feng.

64
00:04:11,280 --> 00:04:12,520
I have arrived home.

65
00:04:12,800 --> 00:04:14,330
Thank you for escorting me.

66
00:04:14,520 --> 00:04:17,399
Meeting Miss Xiaolan today

67
00:04:17,800 --> 00:04:19,000
is truly

68
00:04:19,240 --> 00:04:21,170
a blessing I earned in my past life.

69
00:04:21,360 --> 00:04:24,240
Looks like my second brother is getting me a sister-in-law.

70
00:04:24,240 --> 00:04:25,040
Be quiet.

71
00:04:25,120 --> 00:04:25,980
Watch the show.

72
00:04:26,040 --> 00:04:27,640
I will take my leave then.

73
00:04:28,160 --> 00:04:29,890
You should rest early too, sir.

74
00:04:29,960 --> 00:04:30,600
Then,

75
00:04:30,600 --> 00:04:32,000
I will also take my leave.

76
00:04:32,240 --> 00:04:34,800
I wonder when I can see you again, Miss.

77
00:04:38,600 --> 00:04:39,560
Miss Xiaolan,

78
00:04:40,760 --> 00:04:42,360
Why are you so sad?

79
00:04:42,600 --> 00:04:43,720
Mr. Feng,

80
00:04:44,720 --> 00:04:47,880
I'm afraid I won't be able to see you again.

81
00:04:48,000 --> 00:04:48,920
Why is that?

82
00:04:48,960 --> 00:04:49,720
Mr. Feng,

83
00:04:49,720 --> 00:04:50,920
You'd better not ask.

84
00:04:50,920 --> 00:04:52,480
You can't fight them.

85
00:04:52,800 --> 00:04:55,120
Although I am not a hero,

86
00:04:55,280 --> 00:04:56,680
I have some cultivation.

87
00:04:57,159 --> 00:04:58,320
In this Luoxian Town,

88
00:04:58,320 --> 00:05:00,560
there is no force that I fear.

89
00:05:01,600 --> 00:05:03,920
He is completely manipulated.

90
00:05:05,440 --> 00:05:08,120
Are you really willing to help me, sir?

91
00:05:08,120 --> 00:05:10,760
This woman doesn't look like a good person.

92
00:05:11,880 --> 00:05:15,400
Please come into my humble abode for a chat, Mr. Feng.

93
00:05:16,000 --> 00:05:16,800
Okay.

94
00:05:22,240 --> 00:05:23,320
What do we do now?

95
00:05:23,600 --> 00:05:24,400
Sneak in.

96
00:05:28,000 --> 00:05:29,160
Are you saying

97
00:05:29,160 --> 00:05:30,800
the anomalies in Luoxian Town

98
00:05:30,800 --> 00:05:32,440
are all related to the Lin Mansion?

99
00:05:32,440 --> 00:05:33,880
They come to the town from time to time

100
00:05:33,880 --> 00:05:35,400
to arrange ghost marriages and take women.

101
00:05:35,400 --> 00:05:36,440
I'm afraid my little sister

102
00:05:36,440 --> 00:05:37,920
is already on their list.

103
00:05:38,240 --> 00:05:40,000
So I'd rather not go herb gathering

104
00:05:40,000 --> 00:05:41,659
and stay to protect my sister.

105
00:05:42,240 --> 00:05:43,000
Then,

106
00:05:43,000 --> 00:05:44,460
what's with the funerals?

107
00:05:44,920 --> 00:05:46,480
When red lanterns hang at the Lin Mansion's gate,

108
00:05:46,480 --> 00:05:48,120
it means a ghost marriage to take women.

109
00:05:48,120 --> 00:05:49,880
When the lanterns change color, it's a funeral

110
00:05:49,880 --> 00:05:51,740
to collect the dead from the town.

111
00:05:51,920 --> 00:05:53,360
I just heard the village head say

112
00:05:53,360 --> 00:05:54,840
his wife was taken away

113
00:05:55,120 --> 00:05:56,880
and came back as a corpse demon.

114
00:05:57,320 --> 00:05:57,960
Also,

115
00:05:58,280 --> 00:06:00,560
what happens to the people taken by the funeral procession?

116
00:06:00,560 --> 00:06:02,120
Will they also be like the village head's wife

117
00:06:02,120 --> 00:06:03,280
and be turned into corpse demons?

118
00:06:03,280 --> 00:06:05,600
This is the first time I've seen this kind of situation.

119
00:06:05,600 --> 00:06:06,600
Before, I accidentally

120
00:06:06,600 --> 00:06:08,200
heard the herb shop owner say

121
00:06:08,400 --> 00:06:10,240
the coffin-carrying procession is ghost soldiers passing through.

122
00:06:10,240 --> 00:06:11,360
Mortals cannot look,

123
00:06:11,360 --> 00:06:12,800
or their souls will be taken.

124
00:06:12,800 --> 00:06:14,560
So we never dared to look.

125
00:06:14,560 --> 00:06:15,280
Then in the town,

126
00:06:15,280 --> 00:06:17,360
how many women were taken by the ghost marriage procession?

127
00:06:17,360 --> 00:06:18,840
What happens after they are taken?

128
00:06:18,840 --> 00:06:21,000
Probably dozens.

129
00:06:21,240 --> 00:06:22,840
And none have ever returned.

130
00:06:23,240 --> 00:06:24,280
It seems

131
00:06:24,280 --> 00:06:26,400
the source of all monster troubles is in the Lin Manor.

132
00:06:26,400 --> 00:06:27,640
I must find a way in.

133
00:06:33,600 --> 00:06:35,060
How many men did you bring?

134
00:06:35,720 --> 00:06:36,780
Don't worry, Boss.

135
00:06:37,120 --> 00:06:39,040
I brought everyone who knows how to handle a weapon.

136
00:06:39,040 --> 00:06:40,200
We definitely have enough men.

137
00:06:40,200 --> 00:06:41,320
When do we make our move?

138
00:06:41,320 --> 00:06:42,380
We can't use force.

139
00:06:42,760 --> 00:06:44,200
Those people can't be defeated

140
00:06:44,200 --> 00:06:46,000
just with a little martial arts.

141
00:06:46,880 --> 00:06:47,520
Then, Master,

142
00:06:47,520 --> 00:06:48,320
what should we do?

143
00:06:48,320 --> 00:06:49,450
Don't get too close.

144
00:06:49,600 --> 00:06:50,720
They can sense us.

145
00:06:52,120 --> 00:06:53,200
Lie in wait nearby.

146
00:06:54,240 --> 00:06:56,560
We will wait until those two brats are alone

147
00:06:56,560 --> 00:06:57,560
before we strike.

148
00:06:57,760 --> 00:06:58,200
Okay.

149
00:06:58,520 --> 00:06:59,080
Boss.

150
00:06:59,400 --> 00:07:01,530
But let's not strike too late tonight.

151
00:07:01,800 --> 00:07:02,880
Lin Manor.

152
00:07:02,880 --> 00:07:04,810
Lin Manor opens its doors tonight.

153
00:07:05,440 --> 00:07:06,120
I know.

154
00:08:08,560 --> 00:08:11,440
So, have you figured out how to get into the Lin Manor?

155
00:08:11,440 --> 00:08:12,440
No.

156
00:08:13,080 --> 00:08:14,940
Then what are you thinking about?

157
00:08:15,440 --> 00:08:16,360
I was wondering

158
00:08:16,360 --> 00:08:17,640
what that Beijing girl from today

159
00:08:17,640 --> 00:08:18,700
is doing right now.

160
00:08:19,720 --> 00:08:20,920
Aha!

161
00:08:20,920 --> 00:08:22,880
I knew there was something going on between you two.

162
00:08:22,880 --> 00:08:24,480
What? What are you thinking?

163
00:08:25,400 --> 00:08:26,320
Scumbag.

164
00:08:26,760 --> 00:08:27,920
You've only been here a few days,

165
00:08:27,920 --> 00:08:29,880
and you're already hooking up with a foreign woman.

166
00:08:29,880 --> 00:08:31,120
You really don't give people any peace anywhere you go.

167
00:08:31,120 --> 00:08:32,450
Who am I hooking up with?

168
00:08:32,520 --> 00:08:33,360
I was just wondering

169
00:08:33,360 --> 00:08:35,760
if she would test the rules I told her today.

170
00:08:38,120 --> 00:08:39,000
Besides,

171
00:08:39,000 --> 00:08:40,799
we're getting a divorce anyway.

172
00:08:41,720 --> 00:08:42,980
Say that one more time.

173
00:08:50,440 --> 00:08:52,570
Stop making a scene at a time like this.

174
00:08:54,240 --> 00:08:55,000
Also,

175
00:08:55,520 --> 00:08:56,600
today,

176
00:08:56,600 --> 00:08:58,730
that girl who called you young master,

177
00:08:59,000 --> 00:08:59,720
who is she?

178
00:09:01,520 --> 00:09:02,320
Her?

179
00:09:03,960 --> 00:09:06,760
She was my personal maid when I was in the Lin Manor.

180
00:09:07,920 --> 00:09:09,320
She grew up with me.

181
00:09:09,320 --> 00:09:10,920
Her name is Mo Xiaolan.

182
00:09:12,120 --> 00:09:12,960
A maid?

183
00:09:13,920 --> 00:09:15,050
How do you know that?

184
00:09:15,360 --> 00:09:16,160
You...

185
00:09:16,680 --> 00:09:19,940
Did you awaken your memories from before transmigrating?

186
00:09:24,080 --> 00:09:26,010
Now is not the time to discuss this.

187
00:09:26,280 --> 00:09:28,320
We must figure out a way to get into the Lin Manor.

188
00:09:28,320 --> 00:09:30,360
This place is affected by the rules of Luoxian Town,

189
00:09:30,360 --> 00:09:32,220
so magical powers cannot be used.

190
00:09:32,240 --> 00:09:33,840
Even if we get into the Lin Manor,

191
00:09:33,840 --> 00:09:35,970
our methods won't be able to handle it.

192
00:09:50,040 --> 00:09:51,200
Feng.

193
00:09:51,480 --> 00:09:54,280
A moment of a spring night is precious.

194
00:09:54,840 --> 00:09:56,840
Since you are willing to help me,

195
00:09:57,120 --> 00:09:58,400
then I

196
00:09:58,720 --> 00:10:00,040
will not decline.

197
00:10:01,760 --> 00:10:03,440
What are you doing, girl?

198
00:10:03,440 --> 00:10:04,320
I just helped you.

199
00:10:04,320 --> 00:10:05,480
Why are you messing with me?

200
00:10:05,480 --> 00:10:06,400
Shh.

201
00:10:12,040 --> 00:10:13,920
Humans and demons walk different paths.

202
00:10:13,920 --> 00:10:15,980
If you weren't lusting after beauty,

203
00:10:16,520 --> 00:10:18,650
how could you have fallen into my trap?

204
00:10:21,120 --> 00:10:22,840
Your vital essence

205
00:10:22,840 --> 00:10:24,920
is a great tonic for me.

206
00:10:26,200 --> 00:10:27,360
Don't worry.

207
00:10:27,760 --> 00:10:30,880
I will be quick.

208
00:10:39,200 --> 00:10:42,040
How long are you three going to just watch?

209
00:10:47,080 --> 00:10:48,320
We were just afraid

210
00:10:48,320 --> 00:10:49,720
of interrupting your business.

211
00:10:49,720 --> 00:10:50,560
If you were any later,

212
00:10:50,560 --> 00:10:52,400
I would have been sucked dry.

213
00:10:53,280 --> 00:10:54,360
Little lady,

214
00:10:54,600 --> 00:10:56,200
my second brother is too skinny.

215
00:10:56,200 --> 00:10:57,360
Why don't you

216
00:10:57,360 --> 00:10:58,760
consider me?

217
00:10:59,200 --> 00:11:00,930
I can't bring myself to do that.

218
00:11:01,600 --> 00:11:02,880
So it's a wood demon.

219
00:11:02,960 --> 00:11:04,680
It feeds on mortal essence to cultivate,

220
00:11:04,680 --> 00:11:05,640
isn't afraid of the sun,

221
00:11:05,640 --> 00:11:06,500
but fears fire.

222
00:11:06,600 --> 00:11:08,040
I've never heard

223
00:11:08,040 --> 00:11:10,040
of a demon that isn't afraid of fire.

224
00:11:14,400 --> 00:11:16,160
You finally took the bait.

225
00:11:49,640 --> 00:11:50,170
Brother.

226
00:11:54,320 --> 00:11:56,480
If we could use magic here,

227
00:11:56,480 --> 00:11:58,140
we wouldn't be so restricted.

228
00:11:58,400 --> 00:11:59,640
Without this rule,

229
00:11:59,960 --> 00:12:02,240
what demon would risk coming here?

230
00:12:02,240 --> 00:12:03,120
Move away.

231
00:12:12,240 --> 00:12:13,160
Burning it with fire

232
00:12:13,160 --> 00:12:14,020
is easy enough.

233
00:12:35,040 --> 00:12:37,560
I have plenty of strength

234
00:12:38,920 --> 00:12:40,880
to play with you slowly.

235
00:12:41,640 --> 00:12:42,770
Today is a full moon.

236
00:12:43,080 --> 00:12:45,360
Her demonic power will only grow stronger.

237
00:12:45,360 --> 00:12:46,760
Do you have any other way?

238
00:12:47,480 --> 00:12:48,120
Yes.

239
00:12:59,040 --> 00:12:59,520
Right?

240
00:12:59,520 --> 00:13:00,520
Isn't that right?

241
00:13:01,640 --> 00:13:02,160
Yanhua,

242
00:13:02,760 --> 00:13:03,480
get to work.

243
00:13:11,360 --> 00:13:12,960
What's with this morning bell?

244
00:13:12,960 --> 00:13:14,160
It hasn't been used in years.

245
00:13:14,160 --> 00:13:16,620
Suddenly ringing in the middle of the night.

246
00:13:17,560 --> 00:13:18,760
My magic is restored.

247
00:13:21,360 --> 00:13:23,080
It seems this rule is true.

248
00:13:25,000 --> 00:13:26,800
Who is ringing the morning bell?

249
00:13:26,880 --> 00:13:27,880
It should be

250
00:13:28,400 --> 00:13:30,440
that girl from Beijing causing trouble.

251
00:13:30,440 --> 00:13:31,600
A person from Beijing.

252
00:13:31,600 --> 00:13:33,880
Why does she know so much about the demon troubles

253
00:13:33,880 --> 00:13:34,760
in our Daqian?

254
00:13:35,560 --> 00:13:37,040
The Governor of Huaiyang said

255
00:13:37,040 --> 00:13:38,520
she is a demon refiner from Beijing.

256
00:13:38,520 --> 00:13:39,200
So

257
00:13:39,200 --> 00:13:40,730
she knows no less than we do.

258
00:13:41,000 --> 00:13:41,880
I'll go take a look.

259
00:13:41,880 --> 00:13:42,540
Wait for me.

260
00:13:43,520 --> 00:13:44,600
I'll go with you.

261
00:13:49,320 --> 00:13:49,850
Let's go.

262
00:13:51,960 --> 00:13:53,360
I'll wait for you at home.

263
00:14:02,640 --> 00:14:04,480
Why did the bell suddenly ring?

264
00:14:05,120 --> 00:14:06,200
It's you.

265
00:14:10,120 --> 00:14:11,280
Without some preparation,

266
00:14:11,280 --> 00:14:13,740
how would we dare intrude on your territory?

267
00:14:16,000 --> 00:14:16,720
Monster,

268
00:14:16,720 --> 00:14:18,680
your time is up.

269
00:14:19,560 --> 00:14:21,240
My powers are restored.

270
00:14:22,240 --> 00:14:23,840
I feel full of strength.

271
00:14:24,040 --> 00:14:24,640
Step back.

272
00:14:25,240 --> 00:14:25,770
Alright.

273
00:14:50,880 --> 00:14:52,040
Before the bell stops ringing,

274
00:14:52,040 --> 00:14:53,240
we must take her down.

275
00:14:53,800 --> 00:14:54,360
Wait.

276
00:14:54,720 --> 00:14:56,040
She is stalling for time.

277
00:14:56,040 --> 00:14:56,770
Let's hurry.

278
00:14:58,280 --> 00:15:00,340
I know how to get into the Lin Mansion.

279
00:15:00,680 --> 00:15:01,840
Your target

280
00:15:02,040 --> 00:15:03,240
is in the Lin Mansion.

281
00:15:04,400 --> 00:15:06,320
You can't enter the Lin Mansion without an invitation.

282
00:15:06,320 --> 00:15:07,520
You think I don't know that?

283
00:15:07,520 --> 00:15:09,480
The Lin family is arranging for their second young master, Lin Fan,

284
00:15:09,480 --> 00:15:10,520
to have a ghost marriage.

285
00:15:10,520 --> 00:15:12,360
A ghost marriage requires a banquet.

286
00:15:12,360 --> 00:15:15,320
Find a way to attend the banquet, and you can enter the Lin Mansion.

287
00:15:15,320 --> 00:15:16,200
Interesting.

288
00:15:16,400 --> 00:15:18,440
How do you know so much about the Lin Mansion?

289
00:15:18,440 --> 00:15:20,100
